  <p>I  requested an evaluation of my child for special education orally or in writing OR  I expressed concern in writing to an administrator that my child was in need of  special education services</p>
</div>
<h2>Response:</h2>
<p>If misconduct occurs after a parent requests an evaluation  for special education services or expresses a concern in writing that a child  may need special education services, the school must follow special education  discipline procedures as if the child were already on an IEP.<sup class="statute">1</sup><br />
  <br />
